-- MVV says EnBW formally acquires Barclays stake in MVV
-- By Christoph Steitz
-- Fri Apr 25, 2014 07:53AM EDT
-- None



FRANKFURT, April 25 (Reuters) - German utility EnBW <EBKG.DE> has formally acquired a 7.43 percent stake British bank Barclays <BARC.L> held on behalf of the company in smaller peer MVV Energie <MVVGn.DE>, MVV said on Friday.

